  "bodyHtml": "\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"paragraph\">Meadow Lea Hall hosted the sixth annual Ron King Memorial Fiddle Festival on Saturday, May 10, 2014.&nbsp;The event was presented by Warren and District Lions Club and supported by local businesses, government, and individuals.&nbsp;Mark Morisseau entertained before the competition, served as the MC and, with his band, provided the evening dance music.&nbsp;The King Family entertained before supper.&nbsp;The event attracted 30 competitors in the fiddle competition.<br><span></span></div>  <div><div style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 -10px\"> <a href=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/6th_annual_ron_king_memorial_fiddle_festival.pdf\"><img src=\"//www.weebly.com/weebly/images/file_icons/pdf.png\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" style=\"float: left; position: relative; left: 0px; top: 0px; margin: 0 15px 15px 0; border: 0;\"></a><div style=\"float: left; text-align: left; position: relative;\"><table style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: tahoma; line-height: .9;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><b> 6th_annual_ron_king_memorial_fiddle_festival.pdf</b></td></tr><tr style=\"display: none;\"><td>File Size:  </td><td>18 kb</td></tr><tr style=\"display: none;\"><td>File Type:  </td><td> pdf</td></tr></tbody></table><a href=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/6th_annual_ron_king_memorial_fiddle_festival.pdf\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Download File</a></div> </div>  <hr style=\"clear: both; width: 100%; visibility: hidden\"></div>  <div><div style=\"height: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"></div> \t\t\t\t<div id=\"478613991933175105-gallery\" class=\"imageGallery\" style=\"line-height: 0px; padding: 0; margin: 0\"> <div id=\"478613991933175105-imageContainer0\" style=\"float:left;width:49.95%;margin:0;\"><div id=\"478613991933175105-insideImageContainer0\" style=\"position:relative;margin:5px;\"><div class=\"galleryImageBorder\" style=\"border-width:1px;padding:3px;\"><div class=\"galleryImageHolder\" style=\"position:relative; width:100%; padding